des:
Want answers to all those burning mortgage questions? We can help! Mortgages can be confusing, and there are so many terms to know. Whether you’re a first-time home buyer or a seasoned refinancer, we know you’ve got questions about mortgages. With the Cardinal Financial skill, you can ask those questions and get detailed responses with links to more information on Cardinal Financial’s website. Learning about how mortgages work has never been easier.

Not sure where to begin? Try asking, “Alexa, ask Cardinal Financial what an interest rate is.”
